59:51.922 --> 59:52.922
Shit! Fuck!

59:53.006 --> 59:54.715
Nathan, get back here!

59:54.800 --> 59:57.176
It's beyond your reach now, old buddy!

59:59.930 --> 01:00:01.430
Fine, right!

