01:03:58.251 --> 01:03:59.460
Sophie!

01:04:01.087 --> 01:04:02.630
We did it!

01:04:03.590 --> 01:04:05.549
- Stingo!
- Nathan!

01:04:10.972 --> 01:04:12.014
We did it!

01:04:12.098 --> 01:04:13.807
What? What did you do?

01:04:21.191 --> 01:04:22.441
Nathan!

01:04:24.986 --> 01:04:26.362
Remember I told you the day
