01:04:26.446 --> 01:04:27.530
and I said we were on to something big?

01:04:27.614 --> 01:04:29.031
- Yeah.
- Today, we cracked it.

01:04:29.115 --> 01:04:31.033
What? What? What?

01:04:33.578 --> 01:04:35.788
I can't tell you.
I'll tell you about it all tonight.

01:04:35.872 --> 01:04:37.289
No, what's a few hours make?

01:04:37.374 --> 01:04:39.542
No, I can't tell you!

01:04:39.626 --> 01:04:40.834
Come on!

01:04:41.753 --> 01:04:43.462
Pretty soon, the whole world will know.

01:04:43.547 --> 01:04:44.547
Oh, God.

01:04:44.631 --> 01:04:49.051
One of the greatest medical advances
of all time.

01:04:50.845 --> 01:04:52.013
I can't tell you.

01:04:53.640 --> 01:04:54.682
Come on.

01:04:54.766 --> 01:04:59.186
