Next year, the three of us together.

01:04:59.771 --> 01:05:01.355
I'm talking Nobel-fucking-Prize!

01:05:01.439 --> 01:05:02.398
Oh, my God.

01:05:02.482 --> 01:05:05.317
Sorry, kid, I'm going to get there first!

01:05:06.027 --> 01:05:08.362
Wait! I got something for you to celebrate!

01:05:08.572 --> 01:05:10.781
Oh, no! What is that?

01:05:11.825 --> 01:05:13.158
One for you.

01:05:13.243 --> 01:05:14.827
Oh, my God.

01:05:15.620 --> 01:05:18.289
- These go with that one.
- Oh, God, Nathan.

01:05:18.832 --> 01:05:21.834
Oh, Nathan! What a beautiful dress!

01:05:21.918 --> 01:05:23.252
Do you like it?

01:05:27.841 --> 01:05:29.174
Try it on.

01:05:30.176 --> 01:05:32.011
