01:05:39.311 --> 01:05:40.603
- Nathan, I'm not going to do that.
- I wanna see it.

01:05:40.687 --> 01:05:42.646
I just want to see it on you!

01:05:42.731 --> 01:05:44.273
All right, hold it up.

01:05:45.900 --> 01:05:47.067
