Make sure Sophie gets home safe, okay?

01:06:04.544 --> 01:06:06.003
I want to see you in those clothes tonight.

01:06:06.087 --> 01:06:07.630
Look at these shoes!

01:06:07.714 --> 01:06:09.381
Tonight. Tonight I'll look at it.

01:06:11.384 --> 01:06:14.094
Oh, my darling, I'm so proud of you.

01:06:18.266 --> 01:06:19.558
Tonight.

01:06:20.852 --> 01:06:24.229
