- There we go.

01:09:42.929 --> 01:09:45.721
Here, yeah.
Look what I got you, anyway.

01:09:50.435 --> 01:09:52.770
I had the wrapping, but...

01:09:55.942 --> 01:09:58.277
It's beautiful. That's really beautiful.

01:09:58.361 --> 01:09:59.361
Do you like it?

01:09:59.445 --> 01:10:01.947
