that's been burning in my mind for so long.

01:11:10.850 --> 01:11:14.019
Yeah, well, maybe you can explain
something to me.

01:11:14.479 --> 01:11:18.440
The reason maybe of why you are here.

01:11:18.524 --> 01:11:19.733
Wait...

01:11:20.318 --> 01:11:24.821
Walking these streets drenched
in enticing perfumery...

01:11:26.699 --> 01:11:29.785
