01:12:14.872 --> 01:12:17.332
while the millions died?

01:12:19.127 --> 01:12:21.712
Tell me. Tell me why.

01:12:23.423 --> 01:12:25.841
Explanation, please!

01:12:27.260 --> 01:12:32.431
Tell me why, old lucky number 11379.

01:12:33.141 --> 01:12:39.479
