the land of the living.

01:12:39.564 --> 01:12:42.816
What splendid little tricks and stratagem

01:12:42.900 --> 01:12:44.776
sprang from that lovely head of yours

01:12:44.861 --> 01:12:48.488
to allow you to breath
the clear Polish air,

01:12:49.240 --> 01:12:55.662
